{"tid":355552,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"想學寫app,用咩開發平台好？","createTime":"2017-08-11T11:22:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-14T01:25:31.000Z","uid":8377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0d05cee02ed1d3e1e29e8f1d30c8861ff0f7d194","tid":355552,"uid":8377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:22:11.000Z","msg":"暫時淨係想學寫android app <br />\n我淨係知有個開發工具叫android studio <br />\n用java 黎寫android app ，<br />\n而iOS 就用Xcode.<br />\n我想知總有冇咩其他開發工具都係用黎寫android/iOS 或者同時寫到android 及IOS 架？<br />\n<br />\n同埋想問下 如果想寫到類似whatsApp 咁既通訊app 有冇d咩書推介睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4ff5e1a894c067a956ba287db202f0cc431d15d","tid":355552,"uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:28:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>暫時淨係想學寫android app <br />\n我淨係知有個開發工具叫android studio <br />\n用java 黎寫android app ，<br />\n而iOS 就用Xcode.<br />\n我想知總有冇咩其他開發工具都係用黎寫android/iOS 或者同時寫到android 及IOS 架？<br />\n<br />\n同埋想問下 如果想寫到類似whatsApp 咁既通訊app 有冇d咩書推介睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\neclipse?"},{"pid":"1260d41630ee79af8585451510336f7944576f09","tid":355552,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:30:24.000Z","msg":"meteor"},{"pid":"08ff569af4f3aed1b46eac544dc531a843083252","tid":355552,"uid":38316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-11T11:31:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://angular-meteor.com/tutorials/whatsapp/meteor/bootstrapping\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fangular-meteor.com%2Ftutorials%2Fwhatsapp%2Fmeteor%2Fbootstrapping&d=LqU%2Biehar3Y0COcM%2FKLbcDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=8f7fe2f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://angular-meteor.com/tutorials/whatsapp/meteor/bootstrapping</a>"},{"pid":"07b18e13f4c0d4b09f9c6987bd29e7988213e558","tid":355552,"uid":134210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:02:12.000Z","msg":"建議寫番native app<br />\n<br />\nandroid 用kotlin (Android studio)<br />\niOS 用swift (Xcode)<br />\n<br />\nkotlin 同 swift 係某程度上有好多相似內容<br />\n<br />\n學識一種就好容易掌握另一種 而kotlin係同java互通但做到比java更多<br />\n<br />\nwhatsapp原生係由XMPP 架構發展<br />\n<br />\n市面上有openfire 可以用<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.igniterealtime.org/projects/openfire/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.igniterealtime.org%2Fprojects%2Fopenfire%2F&d=LqU%2Biehar3Y0COcM%2FKLbcDQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=1beaa0b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.igniterealtime.org/projects/openfire/</a>"},{"pid":"47fe084959722d387c9d4c36ca9bf43e2f69368f","tid":355552,"uid":134210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:06:14.000Z","msg":"未打完就覆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nopenfire 係一個openfire xmpp server<br />\n<br />\n5分鐘就可以setup好<br />\n<br />\n一般whatsapp 功能佢都已經有<br />\n<br />\n你需要做就係寫番個android 同 ios client就可以<br />\n<br />\ngithub上都已經有寫好左 你可以直接用或者再改<br />\n<br />\napp store同google play都有可以下載Client 你可以直接用黎試"},{"pid":"aa7afd8d8d5e7c96e0e25078c731bf64c83c893f","tid":355552,"uid":127292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T03:06:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1aa04370d081a8ee8a12f7c57a2e3410365452a4","tid":355552,"uid":133387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:03:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>React native</blockquote><br />\nReact native 係咪要識 nodejs?"},{"pid":"27c49c544d6d10daa64716d1a10b3b106e3d4147","tid":355552,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:05:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>React native</blockquote><br />\nReact native 係咪要識 nodejs?</blockquote><br />\n應該唔洗<br />\n你識基本javascript<br />\n再直接學就得"},{"pid":"cda57fd48b08f461588fe66e8f31892d30eac9e4","tid":355552,"uid":133387,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:07:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>React native</blockquote><br />\nReact native 係咪要識 nodejs?</blockquote><br />\n應該唔洗<br />\n你識基本javascript<br />\n再直接學就得</blockquote><br />\n3Q<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3088abd86b90b3e46adc33deb4334252999cac67","tid":355552,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:09:57.000Z","msg":"垃圾java唔好學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84301a9f26f40dd1c2ff466bd7cc59b6fa5f3767","tid":355552,"uid":85524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-12T04:13:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾java唔好學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nJava排名第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"272deef65c699ec903ce6539943060337f2d8be8","tid":355552,"uid":8377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T16:44:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未打完就覆左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nopenfire 係一個openfire xmpp server<br />\n<br />\n5分鐘就可以setup好<br />\n<br />\n一般whatsapp 功能佢都已經有<br />\n<br />\n你需要做就係寫番個android 同 ios client就可以<br />\n<br />\ngithub上都已經有寫好左 你可以直接用或者再改<br />\n<br />\napp store同google play都有可以下載Client 你可以直接用黎試</blockquote><br />\nthx<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然你講個d我總未識 <br />\n不過都多謝你答我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc5e41f2e68e1d3e7d184c49aa98f8163e31a97","tid":355552,"uid":122576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T01:25:31.000Z","msg":"識用就肯定用react<br />\n<br />\nme angular打手"}]}